# ⏱️ Task 02: Stopwatch Web Application

## Objective
Create an **interactive and user-friendly stopwatch web application** to accurately measure and record time intervals.

## Task Description
- Implement core stopwatch features:
  - ⏯️ **Start**, **Pause**, and **Reset** functions.
  - ⏱️ **Lap time tracking** and display.
- Ensure smooth user interaction and accurate time tracking.

## Features
- Easy-to-use interface.
- Start, stop, and reset buttons.
- Lap time recording and display.
- Real-time time updates.

## Technologies Used
- HTML
- CSS
- JavaScript

